"""Apply saved AeroLIT server configuration.

This module is the deploy side of ``aerolitctl configure server``.
It reads saved server intent, refreshes generated Ansible variables,
prepares repositories, applies optional interface configuration, and runs
the existing PXE/controller Ansible playbooks.

Functional Ansible roles own real service changes such as PXE content,
dnsmasq, NFS exports, and firewall rules.
"""

